lead_paragraph: Taiwan's Chan Shih-chang clinched his maiden European Tour title after a closing 67 secured a two-shot victory over compatriot Lin Wen-tang at the King's Cup on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Taiwan's Chan Wins Maiden European Tour Title in Thailand
